ActConstitution Act, 1867
SubjectSupplementary Estimates (C) 2021-22 ** Tabling **
PrecisOrder authorizing the tabling in the House of Commons of SUPPLEMENTARY ESTIMATES (C) for the federal public administration for the fiscal year ending on March 31, 2022 in order to undertake the normal parliamentary approval process to obtain funding for organizations to implement planned government initiatives.
